TextEng: Your actions caused no end of chaos!
You'll be paying a high price this time. I can't let you live.
Text: 이번엔 값비싼 대가를 치르게 될 거다. 널 살려둘 수는 없어.

TextEng: Just trying to intimidate you a bit. No harm meant.
Text: 좀 겁만 주려던 거야. 해칠 생각은 없었어.

TextEng: You've hurt too many people with this.
Text: 이 일로 너무 많은 사람을 다치게 했어.

TextEng: Sounds like Nasher would appreciate you being dead.
Text: 나셰르는 네가 죽는 걸 반길 것 같은데.

TextEng: Just for a laugh, really.
I demand you give me the Waterdhavian creature! And your weapons!
Now you'll hand it over for the good of everyone.
You have something that doesn't belong to you.
Text: 넌 네 것이 아닌 걸 갖고 있어.

TextEng: I've come for the Cockatrice, Vengaul.
Very well. Get going then.
Me want the cocka... the cuckoo... the birdy!
Text: 나 그 코카... 쿠쿠... 그 새 원해!

TextEng: You have something not yours!
You cause trouble fooling around!
Best for everyone if you hand it over now!
You give me Waterdhavi-creature! And your weapons!
Text: 너 워터딥 생명체 내놔! 그리고 무기도!

TextEng: I not let you live this time.
Just joking, really.
Maybe Nasher like you dead.
Text: 아마 나셰르 영주님, 네가 죽는 거 좋아할걸.

TextEng: You hurt too many with this!
Me just toy with you. No harm meant.
Text: 나 그냥 장난친 거야. 해칠 뜻 없었어.

TextEng: Okay. You get going then.
